  <h2>Typography</h2>

  <h1>Heading 1 — Georgia, 2.8rem</h1>
  <h2>Heading 2 — Georgia, 2rem</h2>
  <h3>Heading 3 — Georgia, 1.5rem</h3>
  <h4>Heading 4 — Georgia, 1.1rem</h4>

  <p>Body text uses the system sans-serif stack at 18px with 1.7 line height. Long-form reading at 600px column width. Paragraphs breathe at 24px bottom margin.</p>

  <p>A second paragraph shows the vertical rhythm. The spacing between these paragraphs is consistent and intentional — based on an 8px grid.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Text Treatments</h2>

  <p><strong>Bold text</strong> for emphasis within a sentence.</p>
  <p><em>Italic text</em> for titles, quotations, or gentle emphasis.</p>
  <p><mark>Highlighted text</mark> using the yellow accent — use sparingly.</p>
  <p><code>Inline code</code> for technical references.</p>
  <p>A <a href="#">link</a> with yellow underline, darkening on hover.</p>

  <hr>

